prompt:
Add a public interface called IRepository to Domain.calr with a method signature for GetById.

Use this exact Calor interface definition syntax:
§IFACE{i001:IRepository:pub}
  §MT{m001:GetById}
    §I{i32:id}
    §O{Option<Entity>}
  §/MT{m001}
§/IFACE{i001}

The §IFACE{id:name:visibility} syntax defines an interface:
- id is a unique interface identifier
- name is the interface name (conventionally starts with I)
- §MT{id:name} defines a method signature without implementation (no body, no §R)
- §/IFACE{id} closes the interface
